238
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:11,251
tidak usah ragu.

239
00:20:14,379 --> 00:20:15,422
Oke.

240
00:20:16,965 --> 00:20:17,966
Aku sedih.

241
00:20:19,676 --> 00:20:20,510
Maaf.

242
00:20:28,518 --> 00:20:30,145
<i>Jawaban yang tak ditemukan Ji-yeon</i>…

243
00:20:33,565 --> 00:20:35,317
<i>akhirnya berhasil kutemukan.</i>

244
00:20:44,743 --> 00:20:45,953
Kenapa bersama kami?

245
00:20:46,870 --> 00:20:48,288
Mana timmu?

246
00:20:48,372 --> 00:20:51,833
Mereka mengajak makan susyi.
Aku tak suka makanan mentah.

247
00:20:53,460 --> 00:20:54,503
Bagus sekali.

248
00:20:54,586 --> 00:20:56,004
Kau bisa jadi anggota kami.

249
00:20:58,173 --> 00:21:00,092
Oh, iya. Kalian ikut lokakarya?

250
00:21:01,843 --> 00:21:03,095
Lokakarya?

251
00:21:03,637 --> 00:21:05,555
- Ya, minggu ini.
- Kau tak ikut?

252
00:21:06,890 --> 00:21:07,975
Tak mau.

253
00:21:08,475 --> 00:21:09,518
Aku tak mau ikut.

254
00:21:10,602 --> 00:21:11,728
Apa tak boleh?

255
00:21:13,522 --> 00:21:17,150
Ingat yang terjadi dua tahun lalu
saat kau tak ikut lokakarya?

256
00:21:20,445 --> 00:21:22,155
Ayo cepat, kita makan daging!

257
00:21:22,239 --> 00:21:24,574
- Daging!
- Mi-rae, kita makan daging!

258
00:21:25,993 --> 00:21:26,994
Seo Mi-rae!

259
00:21:36,336 --> 00:21:37,337
Sudah penuh.

260
00:21:37,421 --> 00:21:38,547
Ayo.

261
00:21:39,047 --> 00:21:39,965
Aku kenyang.

262
00:21:40,632 --> 00:21:41,591
Ya…

263
00:21:41,675 --> 00:21:44,469
Promosinya cukup besar
untuk ditangani sendiri.

264
00:21:44,553 --> 00:21:45,721
Apa tak masalah?

265
00:21:45,804 --> 00:21:48,932
Para penulis sudah menanggapi
dan jadwalnya pas, tapi…

266
00:21:49,016 --> 00:21:50,225
Kami siap membantu.

267
00:21:50,309 --> 00:21:51,393
Beres sudah.

268
00:21:51,476 --> 00:21:54,187
- Pak Hwang, aku…
- Tak ada tanggapan lain?

269
00:21:54,771 --> 00:21:55,897
- Ya.
- Rapat selesai.

270
00:21:59,318 --> 00:22:02,112
Kalian sudah makan? Ayo makan yang banyak!

271
00:22:02,195 --> 00:22:03,238
Aku yang traktir.

272
00:22:05,824 --> 00:22:08,035
Pak Hwang, soal lokakarya waktu itu.

273
00:22:08,118 --> 00:22:11,496
- Aku sakit radang usus…
- Dong-min, pesan radang usus…

274
00:22:12,414 --> 00:22:15,208
Pesankan seporsi iga marinasi!

275
00:22:15,917 --> 00:22:17,502
Seo Mi-rae masih di sini?

276
00:22:18,754 --> 00:22:19,963
Aku baru lihat.

277
00:22:20,047 --> 00:22:21,965
Lokakarya waktu itu sangat…

278
00:22:22,049 --> 00:22:23,550
Aku bekerja demi lokakarya.

279
00:22:23,633 --> 00:22:25,802
<i>Itu berlangsung sampai tiga minggu.</i>

280
00:22:26,386 --> 00:22:28,180
Gawat kalau dia sudah merajuk.

281
00:22:28,263 --> 00:22:32,267
Karena usianya bertambah dua tahun,
kali ini bisa sampai enam minggu.

282
00:22:34,186 --> 00:22:37,189
Kyeong-nam juga tak ikut, 'kan?
Kau tak kena masalah?

283
00:22:37,689 --> 00:22:39,733
Ya, aku tidak kena masalah.

284
00:22:39,816 --> 00:22:42,027
Kali ini kau tidak ikut, 'kan?

285
00:22:43,070 --> 00:22:44,446
Kau ikut, 'kan?

286
00:22:45,364 --> 00:22:47,991
Tak enak kalau cuma aku yang absen.

287
00:22:49,284 --> 00:22:50,160
Aku mau ikut.

288
00:22:50,786 --> 00:22:53,413
Kau mau ikut lokakarya
dua hari satu malam?

289
00:22:53,497 --> 00:22:54,915
Ada apa denganmu?

290
00:22:54,998 --> 00:22:55,832
Sedang bosan?

291
00:22:55,916 --> 00:22:57,042
Tidak.

292
00:22:57,918 --> 00:23:01,838
Rumah orang tuaku di dekat sana.
Aku mau bertemu mereka hari Jumat.

293
00:23:01,922 --> 00:23:05,342
Di akhir pekan begitu,
lebih baik bersama keluarga.

294
00:23:06,510 --> 00:23:07,677
Biar aku yang tentukan.

295
00:23:09,638 --> 00:23:11,598
JAMPONG MEMBARA

296
00:23:17,813 --> 00:23:19,481
<i>Dia seperti iblis.</i>

297
00:23:19,981 --> 00:23:23,402
Wah, inilah aroma alam.

298
00:23:24,111 --> 00:23:26,488
Bangun! Mau tidur sampai kapan?

299
00:23:27,072 --> 00:23:30,033
Berlenggang kaki
tanpa membawa barang. Astaga.

300
00:23:30,117 --> 00:23:31,952
Para pria harus kembali ke bus.

301
00:23:32,035 --> 00:23:33,662
<i>Nikmatilah acaranya.</i>

302
00:23:34,162 --> 00:23:35,205
<i>Aku kangen kau.</i>

303
00:23:42,963 --> 00:23:44,589
<i>Ya, nanti kuhubungi.</i>

304
00:23:55,225 --> 00:23:56,059
Halo.

305
00:23:56,768 --> 00:23:57,602
Ya.

306
00:24:01,731 --> 00:24:04,401
Eun-ju, tolong fotokan aku.

307
00:24:04,901 --> 00:24:06,486
KOMPETISI KUTU BUKU NAEMO KE-7

308
00:24:06,570 --> 00:24:09,698
Ini adalah tradisi lama perusahaan kita.

309
00:24:09,781 --> 00:24:11,741
Siapa yang asli? Seleksi kutu buku sejati!

310
00:24:15,912 --> 00:24:19,416
Pemenang berhak memilih dan membawa pulang

311
00:24:19,499 --> 00:24:23,879
berbagai edisi kolektor dan suvenir
yang dibawa langsung Pak Hwang!

312
00:24:24,379 --> 00:24:26,131
Semuanya edisi terbatas!

313
00:24:27,716 --> 00:24:29,259
Tidak ada kemajuan.

314
00:24:29,342 --> 00:24:31,178
- Sebelumnya sama?
- Selalu.

315
00:24:31,261 --> 00:24:33,638
Baiklah. Ini pertanyaan pertama.

316
00:24:33,722 --> 00:24:36,975
Dengarkan dialog ini
dan tebak dari kartun apa.

317
00:24:37,058 --> 00:24:40,979
"Pertama kalinya aku bicara dengan pria.
Apa aku akan punya pacar?"

318
00:24:43,315 --> 00:24:44,149
Seo Mi-rae.

319
00:24:44,232 --> 00:24:45,901
Ya, kau paling cepat. Apa?

320
00:24:45,984 --> 00:24:47,986
<i>I Want to Hold Aono-kun</i>
<i>so Badly I Could Die?</i>

321
00:24:48,069 --> 00:24:48,904
Benar!

322
00:24:49,654 --> 00:24:50,489
Serius?

323
00:24:51,990 --> 00:24:53,074
Aku Seo Mi-rae.

324
00:24:53,158 --> 00:24:55,452
- Dia dari Tim 2.
- Pertanyaan kedua.

325
00:24:55,535 --> 00:24:56,536
Ini karya klasik.

326
00:24:56,620 --> 00:24:59,372
Di <i>Dragon Ball</i>,
Tien Shinhan pertama kali muncul

327
00:24:59,456 --> 00:25:01,500
di turnamen Tenkaichi Budokai keberapa?

328
00:25:01,583 --> 00:25:02,709
Hye-bin!

329
00:25:03,710 --> 00:25:04,544
Ke-37!

330
00:25:04,628 --> 00:25:05,504
Salah!

331
00:25:05,587 --> 00:25:06,421
Mi-rae.

332
00:25:06,922 --> 00:25:08,423
- Ke-23.
- Ke-23? Salah!

333
00:25:08,507 --> 00:25:10,759
- Pasti di atas 30.
- Tidak…

334
00:25:11,343 --> 00:25:12,928
- Kyeong-nam.
- Ya.

335
00:25:13,011 --> 00:25:14,179
Ke-22.

336
00:25:15,013 --> 00:25:16,473
Ke-22… Benar!

337
00:25:21,186 --> 00:25:22,020
Kyeong-nam!

338
00:25:22,687 --> 00:25:25,482
- Berapa lama Cha Dong-hwan bertugas di…
- Seo Mi-rae!

339
00:25:25,565 --> 00:25:26,650
Astaga.

340
00:25:27,400 --> 00:25:28,944
- Delapan tahun
- Delapan. Benar!

341
00:25:30,362 --> 00:25:33,365
Di <i>Villain to Kill</i>, seorang staf hotel
menyelamatkan Kwon Yu-ri.

342
00:25:33,448 --> 00:25:35,158
- Apa dialog pertamanya?
- Kyeong-nam.

343
00:25:35,242 --> 00:25:37,202
- Ya.
- "Selamat pagi."

344
00:25:37,285 --> 00:25:38,537
Benar!

345
00:25:38,620 --> 00:25:41,915
- Boneka putri Bona di <i>A Bona Fide Killer</i>…
- Kyeong-nam.

346
00:25:41,998 --> 00:25:43,542
- Ya.
- Kongdoli.

347
00:25:43,625 --> 00:25:44,543
Benar!

348
00:25:44,626 --> 00:25:47,045
- Di <i>Theme Park of Death, </i>Baek Jin…
- Seo Mi-rae!

349
00:25:47,128 --> 00:25:49,965
- Rolling Z Train.
- Rolling Z Train. Benar!

350
00:25:50,048 --> 00:25:51,967
Kau benar. Itu jawabannya.

351
00:25:52,050 --> 00:25:55,053
- Kelas berapa adik temannya Cha Geon-u…
- Kyeong-nam.

352
00:25:55,637 --> 00:25:57,556
- Kelas 2-5.
- Benar!

353
00:25:58,056 --> 00:26:00,892
Berapa tinggi Oh Seong-chan,
karakter yang sering pingsan?

354
00:26:00,976 --> 00:26:02,102
Mi-rae.

355
00:26:02,185 --> 00:26:03,270
Tingginya 175?

356
00:26:03,853 --> 00:26:05,063
- Salah.
- Kyeong-nam.

357
00:26:06,773 --> 00:26:07,983
Tingginya 176.

358
00:26:08,692 --> 00:26:09,901
Benar!

359
00:26:12,404 --> 00:26:14,239
- Mi-rae.
- Kyeong-nam.

360
00:26:14,322 --> 00:26:15,782
Seo Mi-rae, Arapara Garatus!

361
00:26:15,865 --> 00:26:17,492
Arapara Garatus. Benar!

362
00:26:17,576 --> 00:26:20,078
Benar, Arapara Garatus.

363
00:26:21,079 --> 00:26:23,957
Soal terakhir berhasil dijawab
oleh Produser Seo.

364
00:26:24,040 --> 00:26:26,918
Ini adalah persaingan yang sangat sengit!

365
00:26:27,002 --> 00:26:29,462
Sekarang, aku akan umumkan hasilnya.

366
00:26:29,546 --> 00:26:34,551
Pemenang Kompetisi Kutu Buku
Terbaik Naemo ke-7 2024 adalah…

367
00:26:40,140 --> 00:26:41,891
Park Kyeong-nam!

368
00:26:44,060 --> 00:26:46,813
Tim 1!

369
00:26:46,896 --> 00:26:47,897
Park Kyeong-nam!

370
00:26:51,443 --> 00:26:52,277
Produser Seo.

371
00:26:53,194 --> 00:26:55,447
Apa hadiah incaranmu
di pemburuan harta karun ini?

372
00:26:57,991 --> 00:26:59,075
Pulang lebih awal.

373
00:27:01,328 --> 00:27:03,204
Aduh, dingin sekali.

374
00:27:03,288 --> 00:27:05,081
Aku tak bisa mencari lagi!

375
00:27:05,165 --> 00:27:07,542
Dingin begini,
kenapa disembunyikan di lembah?

376
00:27:07,626 --> 00:27:08,627
Ada kelabang!

377
00:27:11,338 --> 00:27:12,339
- Di mana?
- Oh, bukan.

378
00:27:12,422 --> 00:27:13,840
- Itu ranting pohon.
- Ponselmu!

379
00:27:13,923 --> 00:27:15,592
Astaga. Makin hanyut!

380
00:27:15,675 --> 00:27:16,968
Tidak!

381
00:27:17,052 --> 00:27:18,219
- Astaga.
- Tidak!

382
00:27:18,303 --> 00:27:20,180
- Ya ampun!
- Tidak!

383
00:27:22,307 --> 00:27:24,184
Dong-min!

384
00:27:34,235 --> 00:27:35,070
Dingin sekali!

385
00:27:36,196 --> 00:27:37,572
- Akan kutunjukkan.
- Cepat!

386
00:27:37,656 --> 00:27:38,698
- Cepat!
- Di sana.

387
00:27:38,782 --> 00:27:39,783
- Tunggu.
- Itu dia.

388
00:27:39,866 --> 00:27:41,743
- Oke.
- Cepatlah!

389
00:28:26,037 --> 00:28:27,122
Terima kasih.

390
00:28:28,456 --> 00:28:29,290
Tidak dingin?

391
00:28:29,874 --> 00:28:32,460
Sepertinya terbentur batu. Layarnya pecah.

392
00:28:33,461 --> 00:28:35,463
Oh, kau benar.

393
00:28:35,547 --> 00:28:37,173
Padahal ini baru beli…

394
00:28:37,257 --> 00:28:39,092
Aku ganti celana dulu.

395
00:28:43,138 --> 00:28:44,764
Bagus, Kyeong-nam.

396
00:28:47,183 --> 00:28:48,309
Kau baik-baik saja?

397
00:28:48,393 --> 00:28:49,936
Ponselmu masih baru.

398
00:28:50,019 --> 00:28:52,480
Ya. Aku baik-baik saja.

399
00:28:53,398 --> 00:28:54,441
Aku senang.

400
00:28:54,524 --> 00:28:55,567
- Apa?
- Senang.

401
00:28:57,986 --> 00:28:59,362
Ayo bersulang!

402
00:28:59,446 --> 00:29:00,947
Ada permintaan lagu?

403
00:29:01,030 --> 00:29:02,365
Bersulang!

404
00:29:03,366 --> 00:29:05,243
Aku putarkan yang kumau saja.

405
00:29:07,537 --> 00:29:10,749
Kukira kau takkan datang ke lokakarya.

406
00:29:10,832 --> 00:29:14,252
Kalau orang tuamu tinggal di sini,
apa mereka menanam melon juga?

407
00:29:14,335 --> 00:29:18,047
Park Kyeong-nam
memang punya bakat bintang.

408
00:29:18,131 --> 00:29:19,340
Terimalah ini.

409
00:29:20,925 --> 00:29:22,343
Bakat bintang apanya?

410
00:29:22,427 --> 00:29:23,261
Kau lihat tadi?

411
00:29:23,344 --> 00:29:26,848
Saat yang lain kebingungan,
dia langsung terjun tanpa ragu.

412
00:29:27,849 --> 00:29:28,850
Lalu, dia pergi.

413
00:29:29,350 --> 00:29:31,311
Wanita sangat suka yang seperti itu.

414
00:29:31,394 --> 00:29:32,228
Terimalah.

415
00:29:39,611 --> 00:29:42,530
<i>- Saat aku berbelok ke gang kecil itu</i>
- Aku ambil soju dulu.

416
00:29:42,614 --> 00:29:44,532
<i>Berbelok ke gang kecil itu</i>

417
00:29:45,784 --> 00:29:50,163
<i>Jantungku berdebar kencang</i>

418
00:29:50,246 --> 00:29:52,207
<i>Berdebar kencang</i>

419
00:29:52,290 --> 00:29:57,378
<i>Jendelamu yang tertutup tirai itu</i>

420
00:30:03,635 --> 00:30:04,469
Produser Seo.

421
00:30:05,220 --> 00:30:06,054
Ya?

422
00:30:09,265 --> 00:30:10,099
Ada apa?

423
00:30:11,851 --> 00:30:12,769
Apa itu air?

424
00:30:14,896 --> 00:30:15,730
Maksudmu, ini?

425
00:30:16,523 --> 00:30:17,398
Ini soju.

426
00:30:19,108 --> 00:30:20,485
Oh, itu soju.

427
00:30:22,445 --> 00:30:23,822
Tak boleh soju…

428
00:30:24,948 --> 00:30:25,782
Apa?

429
00:30:26,449 --> 00:30:28,243
Soju tak boleh…

430
00:30:36,376 --> 00:30:37,377
Ini juga soju.

431
00:30:37,460 --> 00:30:39,796
Kalau air ada di sana.

432
00:30:42,340 --> 00:30:43,508
Terima kasih.

433
00:30:50,181 --> 00:30:51,099
Apa-apaan dia?

434
00:30:51,599 --> 00:30:52,934
Dia payah minum miras?

435
00:30:55,770 --> 00:30:56,604
Panas!

436
00:30:57,105 --> 00:30:57,939
Panas sekali.

437
00:31:20,461 --> 00:31:22,255
Kenapa tak ada pasangannya?

438
00:31:23,798 --> 00:31:24,632
Apa?

439
00:31:28,177 --> 00:31:30,221
Ini tak ada pasangannya.

440
00:31:30,805 --> 00:31:33,892
Kita bukan di bar.
Kenapa mencari pasangan?

441
00:31:33,975 --> 00:31:37,520
Maksudku, ini. Seharusnya ada pasangannya.

442
00:31:39,647 --> 00:31:41,065
Hei, lihat itu.

443
00:31:41,149 --> 00:31:42,609
- Apa?
- Tunggu sebentar.

444
00:31:42,692 --> 00:31:43,735
Apa-apaan itu?

445
00:31:43,818 --> 00:31:45,945
Seharusnya ada tutupnya.

446
00:31:46,029 --> 00:31:47,113
Hei, itu…

447
00:31:47,196 --> 00:31:48,031
Hei, Eun-ju.

448
00:31:48,114 --> 00:31:49,449
Eun-ju, lihat itu.

449
00:31:49,532 --> 00:31:51,534
Dia punya kebiasaan minum yang aneh.

450
00:31:52,160 --> 00:31:53,953
Oke. Kyeong-nam, ayo tidur.

451
00:31:54,913 --> 00:31:55,955
Jumlahnya tak sesuai.

452
00:31:56,039 --> 00:31:58,374
Tidak. Jumlah tutupnya harus sesuai…

453
00:31:58,458 --> 00:32:00,251
- Harus sesuai.
- Berat sekali.

454
00:32:00,335 --> 00:32:03,588
- Aku tak pernah lihat dia begitu.
- Tutupnya harus pas.

455
00:32:03,671 --> 00:32:06,049
- Hei, hati-hati.
- Kau dengar, 'kan?

456
00:32:06,132 --> 00:32:08,259
Kalau tutupnya hilang…

457
00:32:08,343 --> 00:32:10,428
- Itu penting.
- Ini pertanda buruk.

458
00:32:10,929 --> 00:32:12,597
Tidur saja, ya.

459
00:32:14,057 --> 00:32:16,017
- Ayo bernyanyi.
- Harus ada tutupnya…

460
00:32:17,018 --> 00:32:18,269
- Ayo bernyanyi.
- Tidak.

461
00:32:18,353 --> 00:32:19,687
Tidak, ini…

462
00:32:20,772 --> 00:32:22,023
Ayo bernyanyi.

463
00:32:22,106 --> 00:32:24,859
- Aku…
- Bernyanyi!

464
00:32:24,943 --> 00:32:26,653
Hei, cepat bernyanyi.

465
00:32:26,736 --> 00:32:28,112
- Aku tidak bisa.
- Hei!

466
00:32:28,821 --> 00:32:33,284
<i>Tapi setelah sekian lama</i>

467
00:32:34,285 --> 00:32:38,623
<i>Aku menangis sendirian</i>

468
00:32:39,123 --> 00:32:41,209
<i>Untuk menebus</i>

469
00:32:41,292 --> 00:32:46,047
<i>Luka yang pernah kuberikan kepadamu</i>
<i>Maaf</i>…

470
00:32:48,132 --> 00:32:49,133
Selesai.

471
00:32:51,427 --> 00:32:52,804
Lagunya singkat sekali.

472
00:32:54,180 --> 00:32:56,599
Kyeong-nam sudah bangun.
Kau baik-baik saja?

473
00:32:56,683 --> 00:32:58,518
- Tidur lagi saja.
- Tidak.

474
00:32:59,894 --> 00:33:02,021
- Telingaku sakit.
- Telingamu sakit?

475
00:33:03,231 --> 00:33:05,274
- Aku takut dengannya.
- Telinga?

476
00:33:05,358 --> 00:33:07,026
Hei, sana bernyanyi.

477
00:33:50,069 --> 00:33:52,697
Sudah kubilang, jangan sama orang kantor.

478
00:33:56,659 --> 00:33:57,702
Mi-rae!

479
00:33:57,785 --> 00:33:59,412
Senang sudah datang? Seru, 'kan?

480
00:33:59,495 --> 00:34:02,373
Pak Hwang. Ini lokakarya terbaik
dalam hidupku.

481
00:34:02,874 --> 00:34:05,376
- Jangan absen lagi.
- Ya. Aku janji.

482
00:34:05,460 --> 00:34:07,587
- Hei! Seru, 'kan?
- Ayo naik mobil Kyeong-nam.

483
00:34:09,005 --> 00:34:10,381
Hei, Kak Dong-min…

484
00:34:10,465 --> 00:34:11,716
Kami naik bus saja.

485
00:34:11,799 --> 00:34:13,342
Tolong antarkan Eun-ju.

486
00:34:13,926 --> 00:34:15,428
- Ayo pergi bersama.
- Ya!

487
00:34:15,511 --> 00:34:17,472
Naik yang nyaman saja.
Dia tidak keberatan.

488
00:34:19,265 --> 00:34:20,349
- Ayolah!
- Kenapa?

489
00:34:21,059 --> 00:34:22,060
Naiklah.

490
00:34:22,143 --> 00:34:23,394
Ayo cepat naik!

491
00:34:27,648 --> 00:34:29,317
Aku duduk di belakang saja.

492
00:34:29,400 --> 00:34:30,234
Apa?

493
00:34:37,200 --> 00:34:38,034
Tidak naik?

494
00:34:41,537 --> 00:34:42,663
Ya, baiklah.

495
00:34:59,639 --> 00:35:00,932
Turunkan aku di sini.

496
00:35:01,015 --> 00:35:02,975
Aku juga turun di sini.

497
00:35:05,436 --> 00:35:07,063
Jangan muntah di mobil.

498
00:35:07,647 --> 00:35:08,731
Hei, cepat turun.

499
00:35:09,232 --> 00:35:10,691
Ayo turun!

500
00:35:12,193 --> 00:35:14,612
- Aku turun juga.
- Rumahmu bukan di sini.

501
00:35:14,695 --> 00:35:17,156
Aku bisa naik metro. Terima kasih.

502
00:35:17,240 --> 00:35:18,908
Aku searah. Biar kuantar.

503
00:35:24,455 --> 00:35:26,582
Hati-hati di jalan.
Kyeong-nam, terima kasih.

504
00:35:26,666 --> 00:35:28,709
Sampai jumpa besok.

505
00:35:39,887 --> 00:35:42,098
Pengharum mobilmu wangi sekali.

506
00:35:44,016 --> 00:35:44,851
<i>Diam saja.</i>

507
00:35:44,934 --> 00:35:47,311
Kau masih bau miras. Minum banyak, ya?

508
00:35:47,395 --> 00:35:48,229
Apa?

509
00:35:48,729 --> 00:35:50,565
Tidak begitu.

510
00:35:50,648 --> 00:35:52,108
Apa iya?

511
00:35:55,403 --> 00:35:58,364
- Turun di dekat Stasiun Yongsan, ya?
- Ya.

512
00:35:59,031 --> 00:36:01,492
Tapi bukankah kau tinggal di Seongsu?

513
00:36:01,993 --> 00:36:02,827
Benar.

514
00:36:03,619 --> 00:36:04,453
Tapi kenapa…

515
00:36:05,037 --> 00:36:06,789
Aku ada rapat dengan Hwany.

516
00:36:07,790 --> 00:36:08,708
Di hari Minggu?

517
00:36:09,500 --> 00:36:10,334
Ya.

518
00:36:12,253 --> 00:36:14,463
Kukira kau menjaga
keseimbangan hidup dan kerja.

519
00:36:14,547 --> 00:36:18,009
Dia sangat berambisi.
Aku tak bisa mematahkan semangatnya.

520
00:36:20,303 --> 00:36:23,431
Ternyata dia berambisi, ya.

521
00:36:23,514 --> 00:36:24,640
Begitu rupanya.

522
00:36:25,141 --> 00:36:28,644
Bagaimana dengan Bu Yun?
Pak Hwang sangat khawatir.

523
00:36:30,271 --> 00:36:31,397
Khawatir soal apa?

524
00:36:31,480 --> 00:36:34,400
Pasti soal penjualan.
Bulan lalu turun drastis.

525
00:36:35,735 --> 00:36:39,030
Itu hanya sementara
karena promo koin dan hiatus.

526
00:36:39,113 --> 00:36:42,658
Ratingnya rendah dan penjualannya turun.
Wajar jika cemas.

527
00:36:44,827 --> 00:36:45,703
Ya.

528
00:36:45,786 --> 00:36:48,623
Cerpen yang tadinya akan dikerjakan Bu Yun

529
