530
00:36:54,420 --> 00:36:56,047
Turun di sana, 'kan?

531
00:36:56,672 --> 00:36:57,506
Ya.

532
00:36:58,716 --> 00:37:00,009
Tapi kenapa Pak Hwang

533
00:37:00,092 --> 00:37:03,262
