tidak kepadaku langsung?

534
00:37:03,888 --> 00:37:04,722
Entahlah.

535
00:37:07,892 --> 00:37:09,268
Terima kasih tumpangannya.

536
00:37:10,561 --> 00:37:12,980
Tak ada yang mau kausampaikan lagi, 'kan?

537
00:37:15,816 --> 00:37:16,859
Ada.

538
00:37:19,779 --> 00:37:20,613
Soal apa?

539
00:37:25,868 --> 00:37:27,203
Aku menyukaimu.

540
00:37:43,594 --> 00:37:44,428
Apa?

541
00:37:47,556 --> 00:37:48,391
Apa katamu?

542
00:37:48,474 --> 00:37:49,517
Kau sudah dengar.

543
00:37:50,101 --> 00:37:50,935
Tidak…

544
00:37:51,602 --> 00:37:52,436
Tidak.

545
00:37:52,520 --> 00:37:55,481
Sepertinya aku salah dengar.

546
00:37:55,564 --> 00:37:56,941
Kubilang

547
00:37:57,984 --> 00:37:59,610
aku menyukaimu.

548
00:38:01,153 --> 00:38:01,988
Apa?

549
00:38:02,822 --> 00:38:04,490
Apa maksudmu tiba-tiba…

550
00:38:07,535 --> 00:38:08,536
Aku harus pergi.

551
00:38:10,496 --> 00:38:11,330
Sampai besok.

552
00:38:23,467 --> 00:38:26,012
