557
00:38:47,283 --> 00:38:49,076
<i>Jelas kemarin dengan Eun-ju…</i>

558
00:38:51,787 --> 00:38:52,913
Dasar bajingan!

559
00:38:53,622 --> 00:38:55,458
Mau mengencani dua orang di kantor?

560
00:38:55,541 --> 00:38:56,751
<i>Aku ditolak.</i>

561
00:38:56,834 --> 00:38:59,128
Tadinya aku cuma mau mengidolakannya.

562
00:38:59,211 --> 00:39:02,673
Tapi karena dia di sebelahku
malam-malam setelah minum,

563
00:39:02,757 --> 00:39:03,966
aku memberanikan diri.

564
00:39:04,050 --> 00:39:06,302
- Lalu?
- Aku ditolak mentah-mentah.

565
00:39:07,136 --> 00:39:09,013
Rasanya seperti ditusuk.

566
00:39:10,389 --> 00:39:13,142
Apa aku hanya perlu tahu saja?

567
00:39:14,435 --> 00:39:15,936
Mungkin bisa dipertimbangkan

568
00:39:16,020 --> 00:39:16,979
