570
00:39:19,398 --> 00:39:20,608
Sepertinya tak bisa.

571
00:39:21,192 --> 00:39:22,276
Aku kurang menarik?

572
00:39:25,237 --> 00:39:29,200
Bukannya kurang menarik,
tapi rasanya aku tak akan tertarik.

573
00:39:34,538 --> 00:39:35,706
Tunggu sebentar.

574
00:39:36,207 --> 00:39:37,583
Kepalaku…

575
00:39:40,336 --> 00:39:43,422
<i>Dia memang bukan orang sembarangan.</i>

576
00:39:43,964 --> 00:39:45,591
<i>Ponsel dan hatiku sama-sama retak.</i>

577
00:39:45,674 --> 00:39:47,259
Itu lokakarya terburuk.

578
00:39:48,219 --> 00:39:49,053
<i>Apa ini?</i>

579
00:39:49,595 --> 00:39:52,515
<i>Jadi, pengakuannya kepadaku itu serius?</i>

580
00:39:56,685 --> 00:39:59,313
- Tolong tutupi aku.
- Ada apa? Kenapa?

581
00:40:01,524 --> 00:40:02,608
Kenapa ini?

582
00:40:02,691 --> 00:40:05,069
Kenapa?

583
00:40:05,152 --> 00:40:07,571
Kenapa kalian?

584
00:40:07,655 --> 00:40:08,781
Kalian sedang apa?

585
00:40:10,825 --> 00:40:12,159
Main kereta-keretaan?

586
00:40:12,243 --> 00:40:14,829
Aku ikut!

587
00:40:19,917 --> 00:40:21,544
Ayo kita kerja.

588
00:40:23,504 --> 00:40:24,672
Aku suka.

589
00:40:28,509 --> 00:40:30,594
Pembaca pasti menyukainya juga.

590
00:40:30,678 --> 00:40:34,473
Aku suka penghormatan cerdasnya di awal,
aku juga suka gaya gambarnya.

591
00:40:34,974 --> 00:40:37,935
Meski bukan tren terbaru,
tapi terasa orisinal.

592
00:40:38,018 --> 00:40:39,562
Intinya, pembaca juga

593
00:40:40,229 --> 00:40:41,105
pasti suka.

594
00:40:41,188 --> 00:40:43,649
<i>Aku suka.</i>

595
00:40:44,150 --> 00:40:45,067
<i>Sadar.</i>

596
00:40:45,568 --> 00:40:46,444
<i>Sadarlah!</i>

597
00:40:47,069 --> 00:40:49,155
- Mau istirahat dulu?
- Baiklah.

598
00:40:57,204 --> 00:40:58,247
Aku juga.

599
00:41:04,462 --> 00:41:05,463
Didorong.

600
00:41:20,102 --> 00:41:22,021
Ini benar-benar membuatku gila.

601
00:41:32,990 --> 00:41:34,575
<i>Tak bisa bertemu hari ini?</i>

602
00:41:36,327 --> 00:41:38,496
<i>Ayo bertemu. Aku akan pulang cepat.</i>

603
00:41:52,718 --> 00:41:54,595
- Produser Seo.
- Ya?

604
00:41:55,346 --> 00:41:56,514
Apa aku ada salah?

605
00:41:57,932 --> 00:41:58,766
Apa?

606
00:42:05,689 --> 00:42:09,235
- Tak kusangka kau akan menghindar.
- Menghindar? Kapan…

607
00:42:09,735 --> 00:42:10,694
Kapan aku…

608
00:42:11,654 --> 00:42:12,613
Apa aku boleh

609
00:42:13,447 --> 00:42:14,406
menunggu jawabanmu?

610
00:42:15,407 --> 00:42:16,617
<i>Ya ampun.</i>

611
00:42:17,117 --> 00:42:17,952
Atau aku

612
00:42:18,953 --> 00:42:19,995
menyerah saja?

613
00:42:27,586 --> 00:42:28,587
Itu…

614
00:42:29,088 --> 00:42:33,008
- Aku…
- Kalau sudah punya pacar, bilang saja.

615
00:42:35,386 --> 00:42:36,720
Aku…

616
00:42:37,388 --> 00:42:38,222
Punya.

617
00:42:41,433 --> 00:42:44,770
Sekarang aku sudah punya pacar. Ya.

618
00:42:45,521 --> 00:42:48,107
Jadi, anggap saja aku tak mendengar

619
00:42:48,190 --> 00:42:50,442
apa yang kaukatakan kepadaku.

620
00:42:51,694 --> 00:42:52,528
Ya.

621
00:42:53,320 --> 00:42:54,154
Ya?

622
00:42:55,739 --> 00:42:56,574
Baiklah.

623
00:43:14,675 --> 00:43:16,135
<i>Kenapa mudah sekali?</i>

624
00:43:16,635 --> 00:43:18,137
<i>Mudah menyatakan dan menyerah.</i>

625
00:43:18,637 --> 00:43:20,264
Dasar sok hebat.

626
00:43:25,144 --> 00:43:27,104
PRODUSER PARK KYEONG-NAM

627
00:43:28,814 --> 00:43:30,691
<i>Aku tak mengerti pikirannya.</i>

628
00:43:31,609 --> 00:43:32,610
Masa bodoh.

629
00:43:58,385 --> 00:44:00,471
Ternyata kau bukan cuma jago kumdo.

630
00:44:01,305 --> 00:44:02,139
Aku jago semuanya.

631
00:44:03,891 --> 00:44:04,933
Ayo main bersama.

632
00:44:05,934 --> 00:44:06,769
Cepat susul aku.

633
00:44:27,289 --> 00:44:28,165
Kak Eun-ho.

634
00:44:29,625 --> 00:44:33,128
- Aku terima pengakuan cinta.
- Orang yang selalu kaumaki?

635
00:44:34,421 --> 00:44:35,547
Sudah kuduga.

636
00:44:36,965 --> 00:44:38,384
Bagaimana kau bisa tahu?

637
00:44:40,135 --> 00:44:41,553
Itu sangat tiba-tiba.

638
