Saat kubilang sudah punya pacar,
dia langsung menyerah.

639
00:44:45,641 --> 00:44:47,685
Dia cuma mau coba-coba atau apa?

640
00:44:47,768 --> 00:44:49,520
Mau tahu apa aku suka dia?

641
00:44:50,020 --> 00:44:50,854
Mengesalkan.

642
00:44:51,438 --> 00:44:53,982
Kau memikirkan pria lain saat bersamaku?

643
00:44:57,403 --> 00:44:58,862
Apa kau cemburu?

644
00:44:59,905 --> 00:45:00,823
Tidak.

645
00:45:02,408 --> 00:45:03,659
Sepertinya benar.

646
00:45:04,159 --> 00:45:05,119
Cemburu, 'kan?

647
00:45:12,126 --> 00:45:14,086
Apa aku makin cantik?

648
00:45:14,837 --> 00:45:16,505
Aku menyukaimu.

649
00:45:24,304 --> 00:45:25,681
Pesonaku belum mati.

650
00:45:26,849 --> 00:45:29,601
Ayo coba juga. Hasilnya pasti cantik.

651
00:45:32,938 --> 00:45:35,482
Cari hiburan itu
cuma buat orang patah hati.

652
00:45:38,569 --> 00:45:41,822
Aku sudah baik-baik saja.
Patah hati apanya?

653
00:45:41,905 --> 00:45:46,326
Kau terus menghamburkan uang.
Jelas masih patah hati.

654
00:45:47,536 --> 00:45:49,955
Aku harus bersiap untuk babak baru.

655
00:45:50,038 --> 00:45:53,667
Sayang wajahku jika disia-siakan begini.

656
00:45:55,127 --> 00:45:56,879
- Terserah saja.
- Seo Eun-ho.

657
00:45:56,962 --> 00:45:57,796
SEO EUN-HO

658
00:45:59,465 --> 00:46:00,299
Aku mau lihat.

659
00:46:01,759 --> 00:46:03,761
Dia tampan sekali.

660
00:46:05,471 --> 00:46:07,306
- Sudah coba ini?
- Ya, sudah.

661
00:46:07,931 --> 00:46:08,974
Ini bagus sekali.

662
00:46:09,057 --> 00:46:10,476
- Yang mana?
- Ini…

663
00:46:11,059 --> 00:46:12,561
- Sudah lihat Galaksi?
- Tentu.

664
00:46:13,937 --> 00:46:14,772
Aku mau coba ini.

665
00:46:14,855 --> 00:46:16,356
- Acara Penyambutan?
- Ya.

666
00:46:16,440 --> 00:46:18,901
Aku suka ini. Saat tiba-tiba hujan deras…

667
00:46:19,526 --> 00:46:21,779
Dia tampan sekali.

668
00:46:21,862 --> 00:46:22,696
Apa ini?

669
00:46:27,951 --> 00:46:30,287
LIMA MOMEN TERBAIK SEO EUN-HO

670
00:46:31,538 --> 00:46:34,166
<i>Respons terhadap Seo Eun-ho</i>
<i>paling meledak.</i>

671
00:46:34,249 --> 00:46:37,377
<i>Kami bertemu dengan para wanita</i>
<i>yang jatuh cinta kepadanya,</i>

672
00:46:37,461 --> 00:46:39,922
<i>pria lembut tapi seksi</i>
<i>dan kuat tapi ingin dilindungi.</i>

673
00:46:40,005 --> 00:46:41,840
<i>Karyawan K mengaku seperti ini,</i>

674
00:46:41,924 --> 00:46:43,467
<i>"Dunia nyata tak penting lagi.</i>

675
00:46:43,550 --> 00:46:46,136
<i>Sepulang kerja,</i>
<i>aku kencan dengannya 2-3 jam.</i>

676
00:46:46,220 --> 00:46:48,472
<i>Rasanya seperti kencan sungguhan.</i>

677
00:46:48,555 --> 00:46:50,098
<i>Tidak, jauh lebih indah."</i>

678
00:46:50,974 --> 00:46:53,393
<i>Lima momen terbaik Eun-ho masa kuliah.</i>

679
00:46:53,477 --> 00:46:55,729
<i>Nomor 5. Mengikat sabuk seragam kumdo.</i>

680
00:46:56,939 --> 00:46:58,357
Jangan sengaja mengalah.

681
00:46:58,440 --> 00:46:59,817
Main dengan serius.

682
00:47:01,777 --> 00:47:06,198
<i>Nomor 4. Momen berlari bersama</i>
<i>di tengah hujan deras seperti di film.</i>

683
00:47:06,990 --> 00:47:08,742
<i>- Nomor 3.</i>
- Apa bagimu…

684
00:47:08,826 --> 00:47:10,244
Aku hanya seniormu?

685
00:47:11,203 --> 00:47:12,621
<i>- Nomor 2.</i>
- Ujianku?

686
00:47:12,704 --> 00:47:14,915
<i>Saat saling memastikan</i>
<i>perasaan satu sama lain.</i>

687
00:47:14,998 --> 00:47:15,833
Kacau.

688
00:47:15,916 --> 00:47:17,167
Karenamu.

689
00:47:18,293 --> 00:47:19,962
<i>Nomor 1. Malam acara penyambutan.</i>

690
00:47:20,045 --> 00:47:23,715
<i>Momen romantis saat duduk bersama</i>
<i>melihat matahari terbenam.</i>

691
00:47:23,799 --> 00:47:24,633
NOMOR 1

692
00:47:27,427 --> 00:47:29,346
<i>Lima momen terbaik Eun-ho masa kerja.</i>

693
00:47:29,429 --> 00:47:32,307
<i>- Nomor 5.</i>
- Kau cantik seperti dulu.

694
00:47:32,391 --> 00:47:36,645
<i>Nomor 4. Momen mengikat apron</i>
<i>dengan lembut, berbeda dengan saat kuliah.</i>

695
00:47:36,728 --> 00:47:38,355
<i>- Nomor 3.</i>
- Aku tak menyangka.

696
00:47:38,438 --> 00:47:40,941
