aku tak bisa melupakanmu.

697
00:48:37,122 --> 00:48:38,248
Apa ini?

698
00:48:39,958 --> 00:48:41,126
Dia ke mana?

699
00:48:46,214 --> 00:48:47,758
Mengejutkan saja.

700
00:48:47,841 --> 00:48:48,967
Kaget, ya?

701
00:48:49,051 --> 00:48:50,093
Untukmu.

702
00:48:52,346 --> 00:48:54,723
Bunga untuk apa? Ini hari spesial?

703
00:48:54,806 --> 00:48:55,891
Di hari ini

704
00:48:56,642 --> 00:48:57,976
aku ingin memberimu bunga.

705
00:49:02,648 --> 00:49:03,482
Kau tak suka?

706
00:49:06,610 --> 00:49:08,445
Tidak. Terima kasih.

707
00:49:40,769 --> 00:49:41,687
Hari ini kenapa?

708
00:49:42,688 --> 00:49:44,690
Kau tak banyak bicara saat makan.

709
00:49:47,317 --> 00:49:48,402
Apanya?

710
00:49:50,153 --> 00:49:51,029
Kau baik-baik saja?

711
00:49:52,823 --> 00:49:53,657
Ya.

712
00:49:54,157 --> 00:49:55,283
Aku baik-baik saja.

713
00:50:06,044 --> 00:50:06,878
Mi-rae.

714
00:50:09,965 --> 00:50:10,799
Ya.

715
00:50:15,053 --> 00:50:16,013
